        <updateDate>2021-04-30T14:53:03Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Temporary Extension of Fentanyl Scheduling Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill extends until July 6, 2022, the temporary scheduling order issued by the Drug Enforcement Administration to place fentanyl-related substances in schedule I of the Controlled Substances Act. The temporary order expires on May 6, 2021.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
